Yes, this is my profile (finally)

LR2 - MyAnimeList - YouTube - Steam


Why Yomiel?
That's because a friend of mine reminded me about this masterpiece, not Maniera, you pp fag and i thought it would've fit fine as a nickname.

Y'know, the game i'm talking about is Ghost Trick (this):





...and yes, TheOwnerAlpha was old, gotta change that.
Sumfin 'bout me
Hi, I'm Owner (for some people), just a Steins;gate fag who likes sci-fi and videogame-related animes.
I'm currently ★08 dan on LR2, but i'm not willing to get over that (I'm not able to read anymore on that game ;_;).
That said, I like pretty much all BMS song, toho remixes, and few artists on Monstercat, such as Tristam.
I'm pretty much loving every mania style, even though i used to dislike O2Jam, now I think that mania without LNs would be just an unswallowable rice.
Y'know, things change, and so do tastes.

I don't really have an aim on mania anymore, I'm playing it for fun now (I threw a look on taiko, it doesn't seem so bad).

That's it, I guess. Last note: fucking Italian.
